longBusinessSummary: Kaanapali Land, LLC engages in the property and agriculture businesses in the state of Hawaii. The company's Agriculture segment is involved in farming, harvesting, and milling operations relating to coffee orchards on behalf of the land owners. This segment also cultivates, harvests, and sells bananas, citrus fruits, and alfalfa, as well as engages in ranching operations. The company sells milled green coffee under the Mauigrown Coffee brand. Its Property segment primarily develops land for sale, as well as negotiates the bulk sale of undeveloped land. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Chicago, Illinois. Kaanapali Land, LLC is a subsidiary of Pacific Trail Holdings, LLC.
